1. Masuk ke folder Download
2. Ketik perintah : 
    sudo apt update
3. Ketik perintah : 
    sudo apt install build-essential zlib1g-dev libncurses5-dev libgdbm-dev libnss3-dev libssl-dev libreadline-dev libffi-dev wget
4. Download the python source, ketik : 
    wget https://www.python.org/ftp/python/3.10.14/Python-3.10.14.tgz
5. UnTAR file : 
    tar xvf Downloads/Python-3.10.14.tgz
6. Buat folder build-python-3.10.14
7. Masuk ke folder build-python-3.10.14
8. Ketik perintah : 
    ../Python-3.10.14/configure --enable-optimizations
9. Jalankan make dengan perintah : 
    make -j 4   #4 jumlah core prosessor
10. Install ke lokasi alernatif dengan perintah : 
    sudo -H make altinstall
11. Cek lokasi dengan perintah : which python3.10 
    It should return ‘/usr/local/bin/python3.10’.
##selesai##
